SUMMARY:FAT FREDDY'S DROP (nzl) *OPEN AIR* (Uhrzeit prüfen)
LOCATION:Arena
DESCRIPTION: | Arena Wien - Open Air | presented by BARRACUDA MUSIC  Celebration of the 21st anniversary of Based on a True Story  18:30 doors 18:30 Support 20:30 Fat Freddy's Drop  Fat Freddy’s Drop are internationally regarded as one of the world’s finest live draws\, captivating audiences with their euphoric diaphragm-wrecking music.The resolutely independent Aotearoa New Zealand band formed in 1999\, emerging from Wellington’s underground dance music scene into a genre-bending juggernaut who regularly sell out performances across UK\, Europe\, Australia and at home.Live\, their musical alchemy of reggae\, dub\, soul\, techno and jazz is a raucously joyful experience\, an undefinable sound equally respected on the likes of Freddys acclaimed debut studio album “Based On A True Story” through to their most recent release “SLO MO”.
